Dear Marc:<br><br>
I don't know if I speak for the others, but I feel that I do.  Certainly, I speak for myself.  We have no expectation of you to take sides..clean house..be the judge..or babysit anyone.  Probably, you feel the same passion for free speech that we hold dear to our hearts.  Everyone is allowed to post here to air any perspectives.  The only regimentation is that which guarantees elementary civility and decency and I and We will let you be the judge of that responsibility as is appropriate and in keeping with your authority.<br><br>
We will abide by our words of promise to you!<br><br>
Edward Ramon<br><br>
